Abyss Î²

Challenging the Abyss Î²

Access the abyss by tapping the Abyss Î² button on the world map.

Fight your way through each stratum while you search for the stairs leading deeper and deeper into the abyss!
Abyss Strata
There are two types of abyss strata: regular strata and boss strata.

Clearing the final quest on each stratum will unlock the stairs to the next stratum down.

After every few regular strata, you will arrive at a boss stratum.

You will need to achieve on all of the stratum's boss quests to unlock the gate to the final boss quest of the stratum.

Clear the final boss quest in order to proceed to the next stratum!
status
Clearing all of a quest's missions as well as its target score in the same attempt will award a status for that quest.

The characters used in a quest cleared to cannot be used in any other boss quests in the same stratum.

It is possible to reset a status by tapping on the cleared quest.

By resetting the quest's status, the characters you used in that quest will no longer be restricted from use in other boss quests on the same stratum.

The quest will need to be cleared to once again, however, in order to reach the stratum's final boss.
Traversing between Strata
Tap the Strata button on the bottom left of the map to access all strata that you have unlocked.
Gates
Tapping on the gate in the boss strata will show you the requirements to unlock the gate.
